So, if something turns up--

01:03:03.200 --> 01:03:05.202
Just let me know
if there's anything I can do.

01:03:08.914 --> 01:03:10.916
Take care.

01:03:21.134 --> 01:03:22.803
What did you do?

01:03:22.845 --> 01:03:25.514
